"title": "5500: reward, for God's people",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "5500: reward, for god's people",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>God gives blessings to his people who serve him faithfully and who suffer for him. God himself is his people's greatest reward. The fulness will be theirs at the coming of Jesus Christ.</p>\n<h2>God promises to reward his people</h2>\n<h3>For faithful service</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor3:12-1Cor3:15\">1CO 3:12–3:15</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col3:23-Col3:24\">COL 3:23–3:24</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod32:28-Exod32:29\">EXO 32:28–32:29</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num14:30\">NUM 14:30</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num25:10-Num25:13\">NUM 25:10–25:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa40:10\">ISA 40:10</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa62:11\">ISA 62:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan12:3\">DAN 12:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt10:41-Matt10:42\">MAT 10:41–10:42</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt25:28-Matt25:29\">MAT 25:28–25:29</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark9:41\">MRK 9:41</a></p>\n<h3>In and through self-denial</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt19:29\">MAT 19:29</a></strong> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark10:29-Mark10:30\">MRK 10:29–10:30</a> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt16:24-Matt16:26\">MAT 16:24–16:26</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt19:21\">MAT 19:21</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke18:28-Luke18:30\">LUK 18:28–18:30</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor9:26-1Cor9:27\">1CO 9:26–9:27</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb10:33-Heb10:34\">HEB 10:33–10:34</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb11:36-Heb11:40\">HEB 11:36–11:40</a></p>\n<h3>At the coming of Jesus Christ</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt19:27-Matt19:28\">MAT 19:27–19:28</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt16:27\">MAT 16:27</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt25:31-Matt25:36\">MAT 25:31–25:36</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke14:12-Luke14:14\">LUK 14:12–14:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Tim4:7-2Tim4:8\">2TI 4:7–4:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet5:4\">1PE 5:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev22:12\">REV 22:12</a></p>\n<h2>God himself is his people's greatest reward</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen15:1\">GEN 15:1</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut32:9\">DEU 32:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps73:26\">PSA 73:26</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev21:3\">REV 21:3</a></p>\n<h2>The certainty of future reward is an incentive to holiness</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Phil3:12-Phil3:14\">PHP 3:12–3:14</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb10:35\">HEB 10:35</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb11:6\">HEB 11:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb11:24-Heb11:26\">HEB 11:24–11:26</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2John1:8\">2JN 1:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev2:10\">REV 2:10</a></p>",
